Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我和你看到了一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一样的东西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是透子的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来这里是为了见透子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}「嗯」什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为什么你会知道这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:25.63,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be2}CAFE 风道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这里是你们聚会的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天十一点 我在麒麟馆的眺望台等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等等…喂
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不用去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为什么由你决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他也真是直爽干脆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒是 你跟刚才那个大卫是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在学校谈论过鸡的关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那么为什么明天要见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过 他倒是个帅哥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和这个没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想去见的话就去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过 我还是觉得男人的性格比脸蛋重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以说 不是那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有什么介意的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那么我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他没说让你一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那么 大家一起去不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你还真是少根筋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不懂女人心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}女人心是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不是说了不要随便进来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}还以为你叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明显没叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}懂得女人心的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}既有身高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}又有经济力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}脑子还聪明的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是能看穿这些话只是嘴上说说而已的家伙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 集中精力 集中精力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你的碎片找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没来得及准备房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}本周内会尽力准备好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我很中意那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}中意在院子里搭帐篷露营吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那么 作为父亲我就没脸见人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对了 我马上要出门 所以不需要午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去做什么 约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有点失败 勉强修复好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}看不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你愿意收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}算是今天陪我的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸的处女作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天来这里 和那个一闪一闪的有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}永宫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}永宫是担心透子所以来这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要怎么做才能得到你的信任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}离透子远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是我说 我能解决透子一部分的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只要有某些诱因 透子就会看到幻觉般的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想和冲仓同学谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你会帮助透子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我在楼下等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对了 我们几个是禁止恋爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我觉得这种规定 很快就会失效的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子怎么看自己的才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}自己的才能？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说成能力也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}关于你的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想向透子道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对了 那么单方面地定约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是我不来的话 你准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是那样 无论多少次我都会去见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天有些大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以听到了透子的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 不太懂你的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}毫无征兆地 听到了未来传来的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我的…未来的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你向我道歉就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我以为没被任何人听到的 在浴室里唱的歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 比起这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}难道是我念叨考试成绩的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很糟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}考试成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一般不会问这个的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}体谅一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你相信我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你要是现在承认自己说谎了 我会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}按三秒规则
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前些日子 祭典那天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我第一次看到了图像和声音贴合的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也是第一次听到声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我听到的未来的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我把它叫做未来的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}未来的碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子看到的也是这种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我能看到未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}看到幻觉般东西的时候 总有一些诱因的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有那个的话 大概 会很容易看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}玻璃 就可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一闪一闪的东西都可以 但是玻璃特别容易
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 就这样 把意识集中到玻璃上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也想…看到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}果然 和你在一起 我也能看到图像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之前从没有看得这么清晰过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}而且连声音都能听到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你怎么知道这就是未来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只能说因为我就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就像刚才那样 两个人在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就可以既看到图像又听到声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}知道了这个能怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}总之先给你这个 电话号码
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}难道是家里的号码
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虽然知道那个人不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我却无法喜欢上他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他没对你做什么奇怪的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是有什么人让透子困扰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我一定不会原谅他
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}已经是最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}得说出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么说我也是个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}噢～ 是个男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我就不说别随便进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}作为姐姐至少要看一下气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说起来 前些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我看到那孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你喜欢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}住口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那孩子在医院里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有哪里不舒服吗　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她说是定期要去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}红颜薄命的病弱西施吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一看就是你喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不要随便说别人薄命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呀 昨天见过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我叫井美雪哉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我叫 冲仓驱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 好早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 有好好地保持节奏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}给 喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}笨蛋 别无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好不容易有了好转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要控制住保持好节奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}还有 祐给大家发了短信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一会儿去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}遇见大卫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 昨天的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不想输给他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什么 我听不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 怎么了 小柳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想和你谈谈心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 我想去告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你知道对方是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我一直觉得你们很配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳和小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 雪 好像有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那一定是小柳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你还是先做好被告白的准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}而且 也不知道是不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一定没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是失败了的话 我就没法和大家在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没有这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能自己坚定地做出决定 小柳好了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我会支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢 透子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 浴室空了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}浴室？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不可能两个人一起洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被告白的准备是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}噢 今天是炸鸡块吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}突然想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}鸡肉买太多了 把冰箱都塞满了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 今天去了麒麟馆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 好想凉台上也有空调
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说到麒麟馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那可是满载着我们的回忆的地方呢 真理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}回想起来 二十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}救了因太忘我地临摹展出来的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}屏气太久而倒下的真理的是爸爸我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}听不懂你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被抱起醒来后的真理这么说道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}居然能这么快爬上楼来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}于是 我立刻回答说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是下楼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呀 好害羞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}妈妈 这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}完全不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}如果 只是说如果哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是能预知未来的话 你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}突然说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}靠赛艇大赚一笔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 难道不是预知将来会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}结没结婚这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这些才是 预先知道了就没意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 至少等成年了再说吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她说今天来不了了 拖堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}昨天怎么样 小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}与前些日子那个人来这里的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}感觉完全没区别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我觉得只是平常地聊了聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}「我觉得」是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因为我不在场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你让他们俩独处了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就是这样 和短信上说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天大家一起登山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}首先说明一下集合时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在那之前 我有想通知的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}请说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}恋爱 解禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 恋爱本来是禁止的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没错 但是从现在开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 不用等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 柳同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大家已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这样啊 没想到早早结束了 所以我就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}让我稍微休息一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天的预定问雪哉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}您要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}苹果茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 还有 透子同学的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}恋爱 解禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想起来还有事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 小雪 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能等一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天也好热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 抱歉 有什么事来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你昨天和大卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 难道说已经跟你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}比如谈谈心什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}谈心…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪很容易害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和女孩子面对面的时候 也许不能很温柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 不对 虽然很温柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}心意什么的 不说出口来经常就会传达不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没传达到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对珍重的人 说出你的真心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是呀 不说出口来不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等等 告诉我干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…喜欢…透子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喜欢透子！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多…多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}摆出一张傻子一样的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什么 在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这是我回家的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}走 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}得做点儿什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 我是冲仓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 啊 那个 我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一个学校的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 冲仓同学 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想…看到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也想…看到未来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
